        <a href="/giris" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:42px;padding:0 18px;border-radius:9px;background:#2158ff;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:800;">Giriş Sayfasına Dön</a>
